{"metadata":{"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"}}}